column9: The Capital. Old Havana (UNESCO). Malecón. Classic cars.
'Hero City'. Cradle of the Revolution. Trova music.
National Anthem birthplace. Sierra Maestra mountains.
City of Tinajones (clay pots). Maze-like streets.
Gateway to Jardines del Rey keys.
'Athens of Cuba'. Varadero beach resort nearby.
Isle of Youth. Diving and Presidio Modelo.
Tobacco country (Viñales Valley). Best cigars in the world.
